3.00	Ballade_in_the_Form_of_Variations	Ballade in the Form of Variations	Ballade in the Form of Variations on a Norwegian Folk Song in G minor, Op. 24, is a large scale work for piano by Edvard Grieg. It is in the form of theme and variations, the theme being the Norwegian folk song Mountain Song. A performance usually lasts around 20 minutes.	
